descriptionHtml:
This is my page for ALL my  Retetures of  Jaysus\'s fabulous jaysus swords mod.

Items Edited So Far;
Dragonsting dagger and sword (3 Versions)
Fine and gilded crusader swords (1 Version)

There will be many more to come for people who love jaysus swords but want a few subtle changes to the look of these beautiful weapons, I am happy to do requests all you need to do is ask and i shall consider it.

Version Log;

Dragonsting Versions; 
1. Redwood Scabbard and Grip With Ornate Gold Ornaments And Highlights
2. Ebony Wood Scabbard and Grip With Ornate Gold Ornaments And Highlights
3. Blackened Metal With Black Wood Scabbard and Grip With Ornate Gold Ornaments And Highlights

Crusader Sword Versions;
1. Fine And Gilded Crusader Swords Without The Crosses On

Installation;
I recommend Backing up Jaysus Swords Prior to installation incase you wish to remove the Retextures
NMM:
I Reccomend Using Nexus Mon Manager, just activate and accept any overwrites, but you MUST have jaysus swords installed FIRST.
Manual:
Just unpack and move the Textures folder into your data folder and say yes to any overwrites
Uninstallation;
Just replace the files added by this mod with the original files from jaysus.

You MUST have the mod Jaysus Swords to use this; http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1002

Credits; 
Jaysus\'s Incredible Jaysus Swords Mod for making these incredible weapons in the first place!!
and yes i do have his permission to create these alternatives :)

